{"actor": {"agent_id": "momo", "cli": "claude", "provider": "anthropic", "type": "agent_cli"}, "causationid": null, "correlationid": "24ddb5f8-88b3-41cb-a967-c9c550124563", "data": {"artifacts_root": "_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts", "basis": ["keep-the-pipeline-unblocked", "everything-is-an-event", "evidence-over-status"], "decided_at": "2026-07-13T10:21:24Z", "decided_by": "momo", "decision": "Operator ruling on PJAN-22: the ticket loop NEVER halts. On a blocked ticket, fail loud (publish structured Bloodbank event + NTFY + email fallback + Plane comment) THEN keep moving \u2014 agent exhausts options to unblock (pillar-guided hard call, quarantine the one blocked ticket, or self-fix). No halt-until-ack.", "issue": "PJAN-22", "reasoning": "Resolves the design conflict flagged at re-home. Anti-stall wins decisively per operator: never park the queue on a single blocker. Fail-loud is the observability guarantee; self-remediation is mandated before deferring. Also sequenced: PJAN-22's Bloodbank publish MUST ride on the gateway from PJAN-18/19, not a parallel NATS publisher \u2014 so PJAN-22 stays Todo/blocked-by PJAN-19 until the gateway lands.", "repo": "pjangler"}, "datacontenttype": "application/json", "domain": "repo", "id": "0778c38c-44d2-4127-9a25-ba984fa4d1d7", "kind": "event", "ordering_key": "repo:pjangler", "producer": "agent:momo", "service": "pjangler", "source": "urn:33god:agent:momo:pjangler", "specversion": "1.0", "subject": "bloodbank.evt.v1.repo.decision.recorded", "time": "2026-07-13T10:21:24Z", "type": "bloodbank.v1.repo.decision.recorded"}
{"actor": {"agent_id": "momo", "cli": "claude", "provider": "anthropic", "type": "agent_cli"}, "causationid": null, "correlationid": "9689a4d8-c24a-4405-a4af-1fcfd5bc2b13", "data": {"artifacts_root": "_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts", "basis": ["smallest-safe-increment", "one-source-of-truth"], "decided_at": "2026-07-13T10:21:24Z", "decided_by": "momo", "decision": "PJAN-21 will be implemented at the PROTOCOL level (prompt + docs), not as new heavy code: an explicit post-loop improvement step appended to the Hermes lifecycle prompt in templates/hermes-agent, mirrored into the Momo board-clearing-loop reference.", "issue": "PJAN-21", "reasoning": "A post-loop retro is a protocol behavior, not a program. Prompt/doc change = low blast radius, reviewable before merge, reversible. Landing it in the hermes-agent template (SoT) makes all future agents inherit it; mirroring into Momo keeps the interactive twin identical. Rejected a code-heavy 'improvement engine' as premature over-engineering.", "repo": "pjangler"}, "datacontenttype": "application/json", "domain": "repo", "id": "eea7b222-b939-4eea-88f7-3d592b4946a2", "kind": "event", "ordering_key": "repo:pjangler", "producer": "agent:momo", "service": "pjangler", "source": "urn:33god:agent:momo:pjangler", "specversion": "1.0", "subject": "bloodbank.evt.v1.repo.decision.recorded", "time": "2026-07-13T10:21:24Z", "type": "bloodbank.v1.repo.decision.recorded"}
{"actor": {"agent_id": "momo", "cli": "claude", "provider": "anthropic", "type": "agent_cli"}, "causationid": null, "correlationid": "a5c68358-e40b-481c-b51a-f76b76a18a99", "data": {"artifacts_root": "_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts", "basis": ["independent-adversarial-review", "evidence-over-status", "keep-the-pipeline-unblocked"], "decided_at": "2026-07-13T10:38:31Z", "decided_by": "momo", "decision": "Accepted PJAN-21 after independent adversarial review (HOLD -> fix -> ACCEPT). Moved to 'Complete but Unacknowledged' (deferred-QA lane): reviewed but uncommitted; operator to stage the 2 retro files (separately from PJAN-17 WIP) and acknowledge.", "issue": "PJAN-21", "reasoning": "Two fresh reviewers, neither the implementer: pass 1 caught AC3 over-promising a nonexistent adapter create-issue op; same implementer reworded to always-record-artifact + tp comment + operator flag; pass 2 ACCEPT, no regression, scope clean (2 files, append-only, not entangled with PJAN-17). Left in review/unack lane per Momo close policy rather than Done because that IS the deferred-QA queue and the change is uncommitted in a submodule tree commingled with PJAN-17 WIP (operator ack includes stage+commit). Gap surfaced (adapter cannot create issues) filed as PJAN-23 \u2014 dogfooding the very retro step just built.", "repo": "pjangler"}, "datacontenttype": "application/json", "domain": "repo", "id": "ff90cbd4-8294-4eee-94d8-0faffecce59c", "kind": "event", "ordering_key": "repo:pjangler", "producer": "agent:momo", "service": "pjangler", "source": "urn:33god:agent:momo:pjangler", "specversion": "1.0", "subject": "bloodbank.evt.v1.repo.decision.recorded", "time": "2026-07-13T10:38:31Z", "type": "bloodbank.v1.repo.decision.recorded"}
